[0.421345, "o", "---\r\ntype: jira\r\ninstance: https://rustworks.atlassian.net\r\nproject: KAN\r\nissue_type: Bug\r\nsummary: OAuth callback fails for users with legacy session cookies\r\nlabels:\r\n  - auth\r\n  - regression\r\n  - production\r\n---\r\n\r\nAfter the auth-provider migration on :date[2026-05-18]{timestamp=1747526400000} a cohort of users see the OAuth callback silently fail. Triage status: :status[In Triage]{color=yellow}.\r\n\r\n:::panel{type=warning}\r\n**Impact**: ~1,200 users locked out of `/dashboard`. Workaround: clear cookies and re-authenticate.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n## Reproduction\r\n\r\n"]
